The paper deals with the training of neural networks, specifically activation quantized neural networks, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The experiments conducted in the paper involve the CIFAR-10 dataset, which is a popular computer vision dataset, indicating a possible connection to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the choice of the straight-through estimator, which is a technique used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and optimization (cs.SY).
